---
title: Prosciutto Eggs Benedict plus Green Salad with Tomato & Creamy Balsamic Dressing
description: The beloved brunch staple gets an elevated twist with luscious prosciutto and pillowy brioche buns. The secret to success is our shortcut Hollandaise-style sauce that makes this Benedict a breeze! Topped with a fried egg and served with a balsamic-dressed salad, this decadent classic makes any morning a special occasion.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6627c8628637342901e433d7-3eb560a3.jpeg
